Class ActiveExam

  • java.lang.Object
    • entity.ActiveExam
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class ActiveExam
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Entity class define Active Exam in the CEMS system. The department included in our diagrams except for one field which is: extraTime, which used to save value and add to the calculation of the time left to solve an active exam that student performs after receiving approval for extra time from the principal.
